Uber hack is a watershed moment for cloud security
text:
Uber internal infrastructure is hacked. In the old world you would just disconnect the Data Centre from the internet to figure out what is going on.

However Uber has so many clouds and SAAS based services that they are unable to comprehend what is working and what they should shut down, it will take days to figure things out.
